<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/135.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/135.0.0.0" version="26.2.14" scale="1" border="0"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="UbgkZaqfqL72tsLlyIJ4"> <mxGraphModel dx="2245" dy="1955" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml
start
:Open DIU Library Portal;

if (Already Registered?) then (Yes)
 :Enter Username and Password;
 :Validate Credentials;
 if (Login Successful?) then (Yes)
 :Go to Home Page;
 else (No)
 :Show Error Message;
 stop
 endif
else (No)
 :Go to Registration Page;
 :Fill Registration Form;
 :Validate Registration Data;
 if (Registration Successful?) then (Yes)
 :Redirect to Login Page;
 else (No)
 :Show Error Message;
 stop
 endif
endif

' --- Home Page Activities ---
partition \"User Home\" {
 :Display Home Options;
 while (User Navigates Options?) is (Yes)
 if (Selects \"View Available Books\") then (Yes)
 :Display Book List;
 elseif (Selects \"Rent Book\") then (Yes)
 :Select Book;
 :Check Book Availability;
 if (Available?) then (Yes)
 :Confirm Rent;
 :Update Rental Records;
 else (No)
 :Show Not Available Message;
 endif
 elseif (Selects \"Return Book\") then (Yes)
 :Select Rental;
 :Check Return Eligibility;
 if (Eligible?) then (Yes)
 :Confirm Return;
 :Update Book Inventory;
 else (No)
 :Show Return Error Message;
 endif
 elseif (Selects \"Update Profile\") then (Yes)
 :Edit Profile Details;
 if (Wants to Change Password?) then (Yes)
 :Change Password;
 endif
 :Save Profile Changes;
 elseif (Selects \"Contact Admin\") then (Yes)
 :Fill Contact Form;
 :Send Email;
 elseif (Selects \"View Weekly Updates\") then (Yes)
 :Display Weekly New Books;
 else (No)
 :Invalid Option Selected;
 endif
 endwhile
}

:Logout;
stop
